 TAB Report of the HVAC system.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>Tool</span></p></td><td><p>Updated <span>GSAS Energia Suite&trade;</span>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>")
    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "E", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Homes", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Primary Energy Performance"), name: "APPLICABILITY", display_weight: 1, visible: true, html_text: "<p>COMMERCIAL | EDUCATION | HOMES | HOSPITALITY | LIGHT INDUSTRY | MOSQUES | OFFICES | RESIDENTIAL</p>")
    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "E", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Homes", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Primary Energy Performance"), name: "ASSESSMENT PRINCIPLES", display_weight: 3, visible: true, html_text: "<ul><li>The Project will <span>assess</span> GSAS energy performance coefficient of the primary energy (EPC<span>pri</span>) in relation to applicable GSAS benchmark.</li><li>The Project will complete <span>GSAS Energia Suite&trade;</span> for E.3 Primary Energy Performance to establish the <span>criterion level</span>.</li></ul>")
    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "E", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Homes", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Primary Energy Performance"), name: "ASSESSMENT", display_weight: 4, visible: true, html_text: "<p>The criterion requires <span>assessing</span> the annual primary energy of the building by calculating the EPC value using <span>GSAS Energia Suite&trade;</span>.  The assessment considers the net delivered energy and the primary energy factor (PEF) determined at the national level.  Net delivered energy is linked to the various types of energy supply including electricity, gas, thermal, and renewable energy using different types of energy delivery networks.</p><p><span>GSAS</span><span> </span><span>Energia</span> <span>Suite&trade;</span> determines the energy performance coefficient (EPC<span>pri</span>) based on the energy supply and delivery network.</p><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-bordered\"><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><span>EPC</span><span>pri</span></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><span>=</span></p></td><td><p><span>E</span><span>pri_norm</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>E</span><span>pri_ref</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>Where:</p><p>EPC<span>pri</span> \tis the primary energy performance coefficient.</p><p>E<span>pri_norm</span> \tis the normalized primary energy supplied to the building, in kWh/m2/yr.</p><p>E<span>pri_ref</span> \tis GSAS benchmark for the primary energy supply and delivery network for a specific country, in kWh/m2/yr.</p><p><br/>The <span>criterion level</span> is established based on the result of the EPCpri.</p>")
    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "E", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Homes", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Primary Energy Performance"), name: "CRITERION LEVELS", display_weight: 5, visible: true, html_text: "<div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-bordered\"><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody><tr><td><p><span>Levels</span></p></td><td><p><span>Primary Energy Performance (EPC</span><span>pri</span><span>) Indicator</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>-1</span></p></td><td><p>EPC<span>pri</span> &gt; 1.0</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>0</span></p></td><td><p>0.8 &lt; EPC<span>pri</span> <span>&le;</span> 1.0</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>1</span></p></td><td><p>0.7 &lt; EPC<span>pri</span> <span>&le;</span> 0.8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>2</span></p></td><td><p>0.6 &lt; EPC<span>pri</span> <span>&le;</span> 0.7</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>3</span></p></td><td><p>EPC<span>pri</span> <span>&le;</span> 0.6</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>")
    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "E", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Homes", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Primary Energy Performance"), name: "EVALUATION", display_weight: 7, visible: true, html_text: "<ol><li>General<ul><li>Determine the primary energy sources of the delivered energy to the site.</li><li>Input the data into <span>GSAS Energia Suite&trade;</span> to determine the EPC value for E.3 Primary Energy Performance.</li><li>Prepare all applicable documentation.</li></ul></li><li>Calculator<p>A. Inputs</p><p>In addition to the inputs in E.1 and E.2 the following are the inputs required for the E.3 criterion.</p><p>Primary Energy Inputs</p><ul><li>Select from the pulldown menu the primary energy for domestic hot water production.</li><li>Select from the pulldown menu the primary energy for the combined heat and power equipment.</li></ul><p>B. Calculations</p><ul><li><span>GSAS Energia Suite&trade;</span> automatically calculates the EPC value of the primary energy and generate the corresponding E.3 Primary Energy Performance criterion level.</li></ul></li></ol>")
    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "E", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Homes", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Primary Energy Performance"), name: "PURPOSE", display_weight: 2, visible: true, html_text: "<p>To reduce the dependence on fossil-based primary energy supply and delivery network through the establishment of GSAS primary energy performance.</p>")
