ed by the Client (BOQ format).</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Evidence of the use of materials with recycled content on site, such as Material Approval Requests.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>If applicable, update material data sheets of the materials with recycled content indicating the percentage of recycled content.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>Calculator</span></p></td><td><p>M.3 Recycled Content of Materials Calculator.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>")
