).</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Evidence of the use of the locally sourced materials on site, such as Material Approval Requests.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>If applicable, updated specifications indicating the origin of the locally sourced materials and the percentage of local content.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>Calculator</span></p></td><td><p>Updated M.1 Locally Sourced Materials Calculator.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p> </p>")
