    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "M", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Homes", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Responsible Sourcing of Materials"), name: "EVALUATION", display_weight: 7, visible: true, html_text: "<ol><li>General<ul><li>Determine the relevant responsibly sourced materials.</li><li>Input the data into the calculator for M.7 Responsible Sourcing of Materials to determine the number of responsibly sourced materials and the additional incentives.</li><li>Prepare all applicable documentation.</li></ul></li><li>Calculator<p>A. Inputs</p><p>Inputs for Responsibly Sourced Materials</p><ul><li>Input the descriptions of responsibly sourced materials with GSAS approved certificates.</li><li>Input the title of GSAS approved certificates of the responsibly sourced materials.</li></ul><p>B. Calculations</p><ul><li>(X) = number of responsibly sourced materials.</li><li>M.7 criterion level = the generated criterion level for M.7 Responsible Sourcing of Materials based on the specified range from the criterion levels.</li><li>Incentive score (%) = 0.33% per material up to a maximum of 1%.</li></ul></li></ol>")
    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "M", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Homes", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Responsible Sourcing of Materials"), name: "PURPOSE", display_weight: 2, visible: true, html_text: "<p>To use certified responsibly sourced materials.</p>")
