ost of reusing structural elements as per design, such as excerpts of up to date monthly certification approved by the Client (BOQ format).</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Evidence of demolishing the existing structure and building it anew, such as cost estimates and excerpts of up to date monthly certification approved by the Client (BOQ format).</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Relevant as-built drawings and specifications showing the reused existing structural elements.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>List of reused structural elements and its area take-offs.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>Calculator</span></p></td><td><p>Updated M.5 Existing Structure Reuse Calculator.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p> </p>")
