    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "MO", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Offices", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Systems Commissioning"), name: "EVALUATION", display_weight: 7, visible: true, html_text: "<ol><li>General<ul><li>Confirm the provision of a commissioning report or plan that outlines the scope of works and process adopted for commissioning.</li><li>Determine the systems to be commissioned.</li><li>Illustrate in the presentation materials or diagrams the commissioning process adopted for the design, construction, and operations of the facilities.</li><li>Prepare all applicable documentation.</li></ul></li></ol>")
