ated specifications of waste storage and collection areas/s and on-site composting facilities, when applicable.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Relevant as-built drawings.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>Plan</span></p></td><td><p>Updated Waste Management Plan, when applicable.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>")
