    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "S", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Mosques", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Biodiversity Preservation"), name: "EVALUATION", display_weight: 7, visible: true, html_text: "<ol><li>General<ul><li>Partial compliance for this criterion is associated with the plan demonstrates preservation or enhancement of either the plants or habitats of the endangered animals.</li><li>Full compliance for this criterion is associated with the plan establishes the inventory of the plants and endangered animals, assesses the potential impacts of the development to the ecosystem, and describes the post-development conservation, restoration, or enhancement strategies of the site&rsquo;s biodiversity.</li><li>Engage a specialist in evaluating the site for the existence of plants and habitats of endangered animals.</li><li>Determine the potential for the development to damage the ecosystem&rsquo;s interaction with the site and the surrounding areas.</li><li>Determine the strategies to enhance protect or preserve plant species and endangered animals, including their habitats as a result of the development.</li><li>Prepare all applicable documentation and obtain relevant permits.</li></ul></li></ol>")
