criterion assessment.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Relevant as-built drawings.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>Calculator</span></p></td><td><p>Updated UC.6 Neighborhood Acoustics Calculator.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p> </p>")
    SchemeCriterionText.create!(scheme_criterion: SchemeCriterion.find_by(scheme_category: SchemeCategory.find_by(code: "UC", scheme: Scheme.find_by(name: "Commercial", gsas_document: "GSAS Building Typologies_Assessment_2019_14.html", gsas_version: "2019", certificate_type: Certificate.certificate_types[:design_type], renovation: false)), name: "Proximity to Amenities"), name: "APPLICABILITY", display_weight: 1, visible: true, html_text: "<p>COMMERCIAL | EDUCATION | HOMES | HOSPITALITY | <span>LIGHT INDUSTRY</span> | <span>MOSQUES</span> | OFFICES | RESIDENTIAL</p>")
