able, updated specifications and other applicable documents demonstrating the required infrastructure has the capacity to support the additional load of the proposed development</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span>Calculator</span></p></td><td><p>Updated UC.1 Proximity to Infrastructure Calculator.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>")
